Mission.Title: C7M12sanitizedHERCFIXED final
Mission.Comments:
CAMPAIGN 7: NEOFEUDAL SANDLORDS MISSION 12: PLANES, TRAINS, AND AUTOPILOTED TURK HERCS
Last week, we supported a Benzos merc ground force in a major offensive operation to secure critical AI infrastructure. They were extraordinarily successful and a high volume of looted tech equipment has been coursing through our base at Incirlik.
We've seen that Benzos himself is a monster decided to quit and rob him in the process.
First, we're going to send up SEAD and strike elements to [TBD in Discord] airbase to clear it. Rotary will clear Hatay airbase of any Benzos' mercs and sling load any loot found in the area directly to the strip for hercloading.
Next, we are going to casually load up as many of Benzos' C-130's in Incirlik as we can tow to our staging area and stuff them full of everything we're taking with us.
The hercs will land at Hatay, load up racks from the truckloads of data center loot stockpiled there, then head out to our target airbase.
Company Objective: Clear Hatay and target airbases of SAM coverage and ground units, escort hercs to Hatay, then to target airbase.
Company Secondary Objective: Sling load any found loot around Hatay to the C-130's airstrip before they get there or to the Tarawa after they load up and go.
Weather: Clear, 23degC, light wind Mission Local Time: 1100
